      <h2 class="pwr-sec-cta__title pwr-sec-cta__title--vertical pwr-sec__title--narrow pwr--toc-ignore">What It's All About</h2>
      
      
      <span class="pwr-rich-text pwr-sec-cta__desc pwr-sec-cta__desc--vertical" style="max-width: 850px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;"><p style="font-size: 21px;">In every corner of the Twin Cities Metro Area there's a hacker, builder, artist, engineer, and entrepreneur whose efforts power the future economic vitality of this great state. During this week, we celebrate their efforts in the form of attention, praise, and investment... if you feel so bold. It's an entire week of Minnesota-made innovations on display.<br><br>Welcome to Twin Cities Startup Week!</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p></span>
      
      
